  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat until shimmering.",
    "Add the diced red bell pepper and sauté for 3 minutes until it begins to soften.",
    "Stir in the corn kernels, black beans, smoked paprika, cumin, and chili powder, cooking for 5 minutes until the corn is lightly browned.",
    "Season the mixture with salt, pepper, and lime juice, stirring to combine all flavors.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a bowl, garnish with chopped cilantro, and serve immediately."
